text: Pogonocherus pictus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Fall in 1910. It is known from Canada and the United States.BioLib.cz - Pogonocherus pictus. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Pogonocherini Category:Beetles described in 1910
title: Pogonocherus pictus
